metadata.name: DANCING QU33N #1
metadata.description: Start your Metaverse fashion journey with Diverge. The first high-end fashion wearables for the CloneX avatars. Now, the holders can dress-up their CloneX in exclusive outfits and play with their digital identity. Diverge aims to inspire the Web3 community to start experimenting with digital fashion, opening up the opportunity for self-expression.
